00:10:32.690 --> 00:10:36.850
We'll discuss those, try to
figure out why did they evolve

00:10:36.850 --> 00:10:40.000
and what is their role
in being able to see

00:10:40.000 --> 00:10:43.400
the world in realistic fashion.

00:10:43.400 --> 00:10:46.520
Then we're going to talk about
